What Type Of Dog Are You?

Discover your canine counterpart with the fun-filled quiz, "What Type Of Dog Are You?" This engaging personality test invites you to explore which dog breed aligns with your traits and style. Answer a series of entertaining questions designed for both dog and cat lovers alike, and enjoy an amusing experience testing your animal affinity.
